  "text": "Animals were placed on a custom-made wire lid (0.8 cm spacing) and cautiously turned upside down, 60 cm above a straw-covered bottom [CITATION_1] . After training for three consecutive times of at least 180 s the latency to fall was measured. The mean of three trials was recorded.",
